  "firstAcquaintance": "A slave who suffered horrific abuse. Her eyes are vacant, her reactions sluggish. Slave traders call her \"the corpse.\"",
  "personality": "Like a puppet, she has almost no response to external stimuli and can only follow simple commands.",
  "like": "Violin",
  "familiarData": "In her early childhood, after her parents lost the wanderer group they relied on, they sold Yier to slave hunters in exchange for food.\nIn the dungeon, Yier suffered physical and mental abuse from her slave owner. At first, Yier resisted fiercely, only to face even harsher abuse. She spent her days hoping her parents or the gods would come to save her. But as time passed, the endless abuse and indiscriminate drug injections caused her mind to collapse. Now, she no longer shows any clear response to abuse or any instructions given to her.\nWhen Yier stares blankly into the distance, perhaps deep in her heart, she is still waiting for her parents to come.",
